text: Hi sorry for digressing a bit   I am currently analysing an employees layoff dataset available on¬†kaggle. It has 1574 records and 9 columns, one of the columns name "Total_laid_off" (how many employees were laid off from the organisation,datatype: Int), it has 442 records with missing values. what should I do in this case to treat the missing values? should I replace them with median value or shall I drop missing values from the dataset?
